Version 1rc1 - released 2015-03-05
* lifted requirements to CMSimple_XH >= 1.6 and PHP >= 5.2.0
* made initialization fully automatic
* several minor improvements

Version 1beta2 - released 2013-05-01
* got rid of jQuery
* got rid of image server script
* removed config option "folder images" (not needed anymore)
* changed unit of config option "interval" to seconds
* removed plugin stylesheet
* updated English user manual
* added German localization and user manual
* added version.nfo
* refactored to view/controller architecture

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-04-07
* initial release
